Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.72,0:24:25.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next time: Run Around.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.92,0:24:29.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, don't call me Dotachin.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.04,0:24:29.17,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ただし オレのことをドタチンとは呼ぶなよ
